{"tid":274689,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"僱主批年輕人「不OT假日關手機不能捱罵受氣」","createTime":"2017-06-07T13:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T10:21:29.000Z","uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf3b74f65fb7ccd0c76972a1e048b5743d95fce2","tid":274689,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:23:52.000Z","msg":"時下部分年輕人的辭職心態，這個小故事引起不少中層主管共鳴，會心微笑。每個行業樹大有枯枝，有勤奮的、也有得過且過的員工。不過，幾可肯定年輕一代的就業心態，的確加大了資方招聘員工和主管的人事管理難度。綜合不同行業的僱主和管理層的說法，不少年輕人的職場態度可歸納三大特色：一是講求生活和工作的平衡，工時不可長，OT免問，假日關手機，慎防給上司找着處理公事；二是愛新鮮，有些每隔半年至一年就轉換工作，工作如「遊學」心態，無職場生涯的規劃；三是做事以己為中心，工作不能捱罵受氣，自覺做錯做漏是應份的，因上司的職能是「包底」"},{"pid":"1641f3f80984d714c9fc9e12b12312b26ee5c535","tid":274689,"uid":66494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:24:53.000Z","msg":"嗯～等我估下係咩報先"},{"pid":"60230b0e1ef549bc54e1da338072576d91fe8ea4","tid":274689,"uid":3190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31385095832a7c77949a3002c9212062230e5cfd","tid":274689,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"你出幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151a7b79e4487d1c74eab96c65c5b9c62ff266e3","tid":274689,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:31:46.000Z","msg":"我老闆真係屌過我收工放假唔睇whatsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07fd819bdaa516641e2f79505d39bf927c494ca","tid":274689,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:35:07.000Z","msg":"份糧有包假期咪睇埋囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c0e34cf20eda0f48f093d2c936174302784d50","tid":274689,"uid":37283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老闆真係屌過我收工放假唔睇whatsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm